column2:
"What a demonstration.
I can't even be envious of the
difference between us."

"For me, if there are 60 of them...no wait,
65 of them, I think that it's possible for
me to strike them down swiftly."

"But if it's 70 of them, it feels like my
confidence is lost just by looking at
your actions."

"But I am a man who will step up to it
when the time is right. Do keep a
lookout for me. Thank you!"

"見上げたモンだぜ。
こうまで格が違うと嫉妬もできねーよ。"

"オレも６０体……
いや６５体ぐれーなら
イケイケドンドンでイケると思うんだ。"

"でも７０体となると
おたくの動きを見てたら
自信なくしそうになったぜ。"

"だがオレもヤル時はヤル男だからよ。
まあ見ててくれ。ありがとうよ！"
